WEBVTT

00:03:55.792 --> 00:04:00.268
We need people who truly
understand the experience

00:04:00.292 --> 00:04:04.143
and represent the diversity
of our stakeholders.

00:04:04.167 --> 00:04:08.018
Corporate boards can learn a thing or two
from the nonprofit world.

00:04:08.042 --> 00:04:11.018
I chair a charity, Teach First.

00:04:11.042 --> 00:04:14.393
It's an educational charity
that produces outstanding teachers

00:04:14.417 --> 00:04:15.893
and schools.

00:04:15.917 --> 00:04:19.250
Our board includes a wide range of skills:

00:04:20.667 --> 00:04:23.059
former civil servants,

00:04:23.083 --> 00:04:26.643
activists, teachers, ambassadors,

00:04:26.667 --> 00:04:28.101
technologists.

